One of the most concerning trends we've spotted around UK COVID is the cry of "I'm not an anti-vaxxer, but..." (see attached screenshot).

@multiplebears, Kristina, and I take a deep dive into why this attitude is prevalent and lessons learned from earlier COVID disinfo waves. https://t.co/ZvB48usDnW https://t.co/5dkRwv9Wtn
